This is a script to play MyShops game on Facebook: https://apps.facebook.com/myshopsgame/

HOW TO USE:
1. open my shops game in chrome 
2. right click => Inspect Element => Network tab (=> Other sub tab)
3. delight a customer, then copy "Request Header" to a file "header", copy "POST Data" to file "data"
4. python android.py data header

any problem on this, tell me var mail: liruqi at gmail.com

